# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.4.2] - 2024-05-04

### Fixed

- minor issues

## [0.4.1] - 2024-05-04

### Fixed

- version codename fetch

## [0.4.0] - 2024-05-04

### Added

- cli option "-b" to select network bridge, e.g. ./build.sh -b vmbr2
- cli option "-c" to select cpu number, e.g. ./build.sh -c 4
- cli option "-d" to select distro version, e.g. ./build.sh -d 24.04
- cli option "-i" to select vm id, e.g. ./build.sh -i 7000
- cli option "-m" to select vm memory in MiB, e.g. ./build.sh -m 2048
- cli option "-s" to select vm storage pool, e.g. ./build.sh -s local-lvm
- cli option "-S" to select vm disk size (will sum to 2.2G base disk), e.g. ./build.sh -S +6G (plus sign required)

### Changed

- cli options parsed with getopts

## [0.3.0] - 2024-05-03

### Added

- Add new variables
- Updated documentation

### Fixed

- Minor fixes, removed set cmd

## [0.2.0] - 2024-04-00

### Added

- More configs

### Fixed

- Network issue, of cloud-init not get dhcp IP

## [0.1.0] - 2024-04-00

### Added

- First release

